        <p></p><p>Founded in 2002 by Jake, Herb, and Joseph Brodsky, we consider all of our employees and partners to be part of the Novo family. Our <a href="/team/?phpMyAdmin=6L5kW5HG9Z1tCtV4Req75I96uV7">team</a> is small, but each of us is passionate about our role and we look forward to coming to work every single day.</p>
